Twitter is at it again. Among the trends today, is #NowThatCyrilKePresident. Tweeps shared their suggestions on what President Cyril Ramaphosa
must do now that he is president of South Africa. Some of the suggestions are outright funny and by the looks
of things there’s nothing the president can do about them. One of the Tweeps said: “MAVUSO TARRIFS MUST GO UP”          